              text="WELCOME TO INTERSCOPE! THIS APPLICATION COMBINES OSINT TOOLS INTO ONE TO MAKE THE USER'S LIFE SIMPLER. THIS IS JUST SOME RANDOM DESCRIPTION I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT TO WRITE HERE FOR NOW. DEVELOPED BY BLUCAT ON GITHUB AND OTHER STUFF TO MAKE THIS BOX FEEL BIGGER AND NICER FOR NOW AND YEA."/>
